            <p>
                <strong>Smart purchasing eliminates dead stock</strong><br>
                Purchase Order Management Module gives you the ability to efficiently purchase all stock items from a variety of global suppliers through a simple and fully featured interface. Taking into account supplier lead times, Purchasing provides the ability to always have the right stock, in the right quantities, at the right price and at the right time. Purchasing will automatically identify stock demands from across all areas of the company, taking into account sales, current and desired stock levels, future forecasted demands and any manufacturing requirements for chosen locations. By enabling activities to become planned, Purchase Order Software ensures each location only holds the stock that your customers demand.<br>
            </p>
